99l [ /l ] record record-merge
dup /l get 99l eq             (merge: ExtValue override) rt-ok
/d get 3.14d eq               (merge: ExtValue preserved) rt-ok clear

1 2 [ /a /b ] record
3 4 [ /a /b ] record record-merge
1 2 [ /a /b ] record
3 4 [ /a /b ] record record-merge
deep-eq                       (merge: deep-eq identical merges) rt-ok clear

