dup length 1 eq               (zip: single row length) rt-ok
0 get dup /a get 1 eq exch /b get 2 eq and
    (zip: single row values) rt-ok clear

% empty
[ [ ] [ ] ] [ /a /b ] record-zip
length 0 eq                   (zip: empty result) rt-ok clear

% sad
